<item>
            <title>[SOLR-2042] fix woodstox dependencies in solr branch_3x</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-2042</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;See &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-981&quot; title=&quot;woodstox dependency in maven solrj has wrong groupId&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;SOLR-981&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;SOLR-981&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt;, the woodstox dependency should use a groupId of org.codehaus.woodstox and not woodstox&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, exclude the stax:stax-api dependency in favor of the org.apache.geronimo.specs:geronimo-stax-api_1.0_spec dependency as per &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/f02b22dc9d7848/replace_stax_api_with_geronimo_stax_woodstox#bd9168d12ef5b637&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://www.lucidimagination.com/search/document/f02b22dc9d7848/replace_stax_api_with_geronimo_stax_woodstox#bd9168d12ef5b637&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
